# getrange(){ local input=() nums=();IFS=, read -ra input<<<"$1";for i in "${input[@]}";do if [[ $i =~ ^[[:digit:]]+-[[:digit:]]+$ ]];then if ((${i%-*}<${i#*-}));then for ((x=${i%-*};x<=${i#*-};x++));do nums+=("$x");done;else echo "Invalid range: $i">&2;fi;else if [[ $i =~ [[:digit:]]+ ]];then nums+=("$i");else echo "Invalid number: $i">&2;fi;fi;done;printf '%s ' "${nums[@]}";echo;};getrange 1,3,8,9-15,23,4
